[Anyone wanting to read the Lancet paper should look for: Prion
immunoreactivity in appendix before clinical onset of new variant
Creutzfeldt-Jakob disease, David A Hilton, Edward Fathers, Philip Edwards,
James W Ironside, John Zajicek, Lancet Volume 352, Number 9129 29 August
1998 Research Letter. - Mod.MHJ
